          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-1" n="1">A Bard, on whom Ph≈ìbus his Spirit bestowd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-2" n="2">Resolvd to acknowledg the bounty he owd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-3" n="3">Found out a new method at once of confessing</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-4" n="4">And making the most of so mighty a blessing</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-5" n="5">To the God he'd be gratefull; but mortals he'd chouse</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-6" n="6">By making his Patron preside in his house</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-7" n="7">And wisely foresaw this advantage from thence</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-8" n="8">That the God must in honour bear most of th Expence</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-9" n="9">So the Bard he finds drink &amp; leaves Phebus to treat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-10" n="10">With the thoughts he inspires regardless of meat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-11" n="11">Hence they that come hither expecting to dine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-600B-line-12" n="12">Are allways fobd of with Sheer Wit, and Sheer Wine</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
